commentAnnotations.text: Patients do not need to fast for samples at screening or follow-up. At Periods 1 and 2, samples should be collected from patients who have fasted at least 8 hours before any study procedures.
When needed to confirm postmenopausal status.
Additional tests can be done at the discretion of the investigator.
